Lecture 1 Game Development

Step 1 - go to unity.com/downloads
Step 2 - download unity hub from download section according to your choice
Step 3 - install unityhub
Step 4 - after installation of unityhub Download unity editor and install it
Step 5 - After installation open project section
Step 6 - Click on new project
Step 7 - Now choose your template
Step 8 - Click on project name section and write your project name & click on create project

  So, now we successfully installed unity in our system
